=head1 DESCRIPTION

An object that describes a deployment event.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 ActionInvocations => ArrayRef[L<Paws::AppConfig::ActionInvocation>]

The list of extensions that were invoked as part of the deployment.


=head2 Description => Str

A description of the deployment event. Descriptions include, but are
not limited to, the following:

=over

=item *

The Amazon Web Services account or the Amazon CloudWatch alarm ARN that
initiated a rollback.

=item *

The percentage of hosts that received the deployment.

=item *

A recommendation to attempt a new deployment (in the case of an
internal error).

=back



=head2 EventType => Str

The type of deployment event. Deployment event types include the start,
stop, or completion of a deployment; a percentage update; the start or
stop of a bake period; and the start or completion of a rollback.


=head2 OccurredAt => Str

The date and time the event occurred.


=head2 TriggeredBy => Str

The entity that triggered the deployment event. Events can be triggered
by a user, AppConfig, an Amazon CloudWatch alarm, or an internal error.



